    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一开始，我就让你负责监视 但这不仅仅是监视。 如果在你执行任务的过程中发生任何奇怪的事情，你会被要求作为 “异常情况 ”上报。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Monitoring All Night》是一款恐怖风格的游戏，没有突如其来的惊吓，即使不喜欢恐怖游戏的人也会喜欢。合理报告异常情况，生存到最后！小心外星人👽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有三个工作地点：公寓、后室和精神病院。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有三班倒：短班从 0:00 到 2:00，中班从 0:00 到 4:00，长班从 0:00 到 6:00，还有极具挑战性的噩梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您能通过噩梦关吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经常在黎明前报告有外星人！长时间工作时要小心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公寓 - 居室</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286330/extras/6b0b711d537d931f8fb79cee4145c505.avif?t=1759575240\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286330/extras_big/6b0b711d537d931f8fb79cee4145c505.avif?t=1759575240 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >后室 - 楼道</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286330/extras/bbc5d406c83ff2a49d501ff324707fa8.avif?t=1759575240\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286330/extras_big/bbc5d406c83ff2a49d501ff324707fa8.avif?t=1759575240 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精神病院 - 接待室</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286330/extras/a72654c24bb7481fa0db287e215749d3.avif?t=1759575240\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3286330/extras_big/a72654c24bb7481fa0db287e215749d3.avif?t=1759575240 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>直播和发布</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以出于商业或非商业目的直播或发布比赛画面，但请在标题或说明中注明比赛名称。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*本片包含向其他作品致敬的表演，但其他作品与本片之间没有任何关系。</p>",
